# Bank Database Management System

A full-stack **Bank Database Management System (Bank DBMS)** built using **React**, **FastAPI**, and **MySQL**. The project provides secure banking operations including authentication, account management, deposits, withdrawals, fund transfers, transaction history, beneficiary management, and loan applications.

## Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React
- React Router
- Axios
- CSS

### Backend
- FastAPI
- SQLAlchemy
- JWT Authentication
- Pydantic

### Database
- MySQL

## Features

- User Registration
- Secure JWT Login
- Dashboard
- Account Management
- Deposit Money
- Withdraw Money
- Transfer Money
- Transaction History
- Beneficiary Management
- Loan Application
- View Loan Status
- Protected Routes
- REST API Architecture

